WorkItem.Description:
When comparing metagems, it looks like a lot of them are missing some of their stats.  Here are some examples.
 
Efflugent Skyflare Diamond - 32 stam 2% spell damage reduction
Austere Earthsiege Diamond - 32 stam 2% armor increase
Powerful Earthsiege Diamond - 32 stam 10% stun duration reduced
 
All 3 of these are given the exact same score. The Austere shows the 2% armor increase in the tooltip, but it doesnt appear to get applied when equiped.  
 
Additionally Eternal Earthsiege Diamond - 21 def 5% block value.  The 5% bv doesnt show in the tooltip, and I dont see any increase when its equiped.
